name: Gcoin-community
body:
### Gcoin-Community Edition

Gcoin is an open-source permissioned blockchain, allowing you to blockchain-lize assets and achieve smart-asset system.  Gcoin-Community is the open-source release of this system.  


### Contacts

Any questions?  Please contact flew80530 at gmail, wusolomon1 at gmail, zhouer at gmail.
